{"product_id":"personalize-your-wall-space-8-panel-split-wall-set","title":"Personalize Your Wall Space | 8 Panel Split Wall Set","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTurn Your Favorite Photo into an 8-Panel Wall Setup\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCreate a stunning wall aesthetic with your own image, split into \u003cstrong\u003e8 perfectly aligned posters\u003c\/strong\u003e. Whether it’s your car, bike, memories, or aesthetic shots — this setup instantly upgrades your space.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow It Works\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUpload your image\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eWe split it into 8 panels\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eYou receive a complete wall-ready poster set\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ol\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat You Get\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e8 individual posters (1 image split into 8 parts)\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ePremium quality print on thick matte paper\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eClean alignment for a seamless wall look\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSize Options\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eA4 Set (8 Posters)\u003c\/strong\u003e – Compact wall setup\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eA3 Set (8 Posters)\u003c\/strong\u003e – Medium size aesthetic\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e13×19 Set (8 Posters)\u003c\/strong\u003e – Large premium wall look\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImportant Notes\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUpload \u003cstrong\u003ehigh-quality images\u003c\/strong\u003e for the best print result\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eYour image will be automatically split into 8 panels, so slight cropping may happen\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eKeep the main subject \u003cstrong\u003ecentered\u003c\/strong\u003e for better alignment\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eNot ideal for images with important details near the edges\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInstallation\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eThese posters are \u003cstrong\u003enot self-adhesive\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eWe recommend using \u003cstrong\u003eglue dots\u003c\/strong\u003e for easy wall sticking\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ePosters can be adjusted and removed carefully\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDelivery\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ePrepaid: Express shipping (3–6 days)\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eCOD: Standard shipping (6–12 days)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePerfect For\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eCar \u0026amp; bike posters\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eCouple photos \u0026amp; memories\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eAesthetic room setups\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eGifting\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51613345349928,"sku":null,"price":529.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51613345382696,"sku":null,"price":729.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51613345415464,"sku":null,"price":829.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/CUSTOM_2X4_display_image.jpg?v=1781350900","url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/products\/personalize-your-wall-space-8-panel-split-wall-set","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}